249
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:15,280
And so those metrics were very
compelling for the smaller

250
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:19,340
airports like Burlington,
Vermont, or Nantucket, Mass,

251
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:21,920
rather than the Logan's.

252
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:25,430
But there's 500 airports in
