254
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,770
So we had an opportunity
to get to market

255
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:33,410
that we had to get to fast,
because once those airports

256
00:11:33,410 --> 00:11:37,000
were staffed with our
competitors' equipment,

257
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,040
they were no longer
an opportunity.

258
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:41,470
So we went out, and we
